           ACCEPT  SYS-DATE            FROM    DATE
           COMPUTE WRK-SYY             =   SYS-YY    +   2000
           MOVE    SYS-MM              TO  WRK-SMM
           MOVE    SYS-DD              TO  WRK-SDD
