       2202-UNPRESENT-CHECK-SEC        SECTION.
      *
      *    未提供オプションが本提供された場合は、追加設定を行わない
      *
           PERFORM VARYING IDXA    FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL ( IDXA    >   UNPRESENT-MAX )
      *
               MOVE    FUNCTION LENGTH (
                           FUNCTION TRIM(UNPRESENT-OPTION(IDXA))
                       )               TO  IDXU
      *
               PERFORM VARYING IDXB    FROM    1   BY  1
                       UNTIL ( IDXB    >   CNT-ATO )
      *
                   MOVE    WRK-ATO-OPTION(IDXB)
                                       TO  WRK-ATO-NAIYO
                   IF    ( WRK-ATO-NAIYO (1:1) =   "#" )
                       IF    ( UNPRESENT-OPTION(IDXA)(1:IDXU)
                                           =   WRK-ATO-NAIYO(2:IDXU))
                           MOVE    0   TO  UNPRESENT-EXISTS (IDXA)
                       END-IF
                   ELSE
                       IF    ( UNPRESENT-OPTION(IDXA)(1:IDXU)
                                           =   WRK-ATO-NAIYO(1:IDXU))
                           MOVE    0   TO  UNPRESENT-EXISTS (IDXA)
                       END-IF
                   END-IF
      *
               END-PERFORM
      *
               IF    ( UNPRESENT-EXISTS (IDXA)     =   1 )
                   IF    ( CNT-ATO <   200 )
                       COMPUTE CNT-ATO = CNT-ATO   +   1
                       MOVE    "#" TO  WRK-ATO-OPTION(CNT-ATO)
                       MOVE    UNPRESENT-OPTION(IDXA)
                                   TO  WRK-ATO-OPTION(CNT-ATO)(2:)
                   END-IF
